 explanation for the secondary early-time maximum observed
 in some SLSNe light curves, such as LSQ14bdq. This scenario
 also predicts a population of GRB from on-axis jets with
 extremely long durations, potentially similar to the
 population of "jetted tidal disruption events", in
 coincidence with a small subset of SLSNe.},
