  Volume                   = {450},

  Abstract                 = {We model the non-thermal transient Swift J1644+57 as
 resulting from a relativistic jet powered by the accretion
 of a tidally disrupted star on to a supermassive black
 hole. Accompanying synchrotron radio emission is produced
 by the shock interaction between the jet and the dense
