 structure comprised of an ultrarelativistic core (Lorentz
 factor Gamma Ëœ 10) surrounded by a slower (Gamma Ëœ 2)
 sheath provides a reasonable fit to the data. Such a
 geometry could result from the radial structure of the
 super-Eddington accretion flow or as the result of jet
 precession. The total kinetic energy of the ejecta that we
