  Volume                   = {415},

  Abstract                 = {We study the dynamics of supermassive black hole binaries
 embedded in circumbinary gaseous discs, with the smoothed
 particle hydrodynamics code GADGET-2. The subparsec binary
 (of total mass M and mass ratio q= 1/3) has excavated a gap
