 We analyse the well known \msig\ and \mbu\ relations and
 establish the existence of statistically significant
 correlations between $M_{Bu}$ and $r_h$ and
 anti-correlations between $M_{Bu}$ and $\rho_h$. We
 establish five significant bivariate correlations
