 / 50~{\rm km~s}^{-1})^{3/2}(t/10^{10}~{\rm yr})^{1/2}$, but
 the exponents and prefactor can differ slightly depending
 on the details of loss cone refilling. Current tidal
 disruption event rates predicted from this mechanism are
 consistent with observations.},
