  Abstract                 = {Using archival Sloan Digital Sky Survey (SDSS) multi-epoch
 imaging data (Stripe 82), we have searched for the tidal
 disruption of stars by supermassive black holes in
 non-active galaxies. Two candidate tidal disruption events
 (TDEs) are identified. The TDE flares have optical
